      "body" : "This might be a nice generic Utility function, but the fact is, it is still not efficient. Consider in-place sorting by making sure you have your set in the right container to begin with. Also consider usage of the TreeSet as a direct container of your data. If your data needs to be unique anyhow, and you need a Set, then use the TreeSet, catches two flies in one swat."
